RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.PARTICIPANT CUSTOMER_NO, B.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT A, /*STTMS_CUSTOMER B */ (SELECT CUSTOMER_NO CUSTOMER_NO, SHORT_NAME CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER where RECORD_STAT ='O' and AUTH_STAT ='A' UNION SELECT POSITION_IDENTIFIER CUSTOMER_NO, POSITION_IDENTIFIER_DESC CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM TLTMS_POSITION_IDENTIFIER where RECORD_STAT ='O' and AUTH_STAT ='A') B WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CONTRACT_TYPE = 'TR' AND B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.PARTICIPANT AND EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CONTRACT_TYPE = 'TR')

SELECT A.PARTICIPANT CUSTOMER_NO, B.CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT A, /*STTMS_CUSTOMER B */ (SELECT CUSTOMER_NO CUSTOMER_NO, SHORT_NAME CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER where RECORD_STAT ='O' and AUTH_STAT ='A' UNION SELECT POSITION_IDENTIFIER CUSTOMER_NO, POSITION_IDENTIFIER_DESC CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM TLTMS_POSITION_IDENTIFIER where RECORD_STAT ='O' and AUTH_STAT ='A') B WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CONTRACT_TYPE = 'TR' AND B.CUSTOMER_NO = A.PARTICIPANT AND EVENT_SEQ_NO = (SELECT MAX(EVENT_SEQ_NO) FROM LBTBS_CONTRACT_PARTICIPANT WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND CONTRACT_TYPE = 'TR')
